cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper is about learning flexible kernel structures for Gaussian processes using neural networks. The main focus is on machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG), as well as computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses Bayesian optimization, which falls under the systems and control (cs.SY) category.
